name: Jane Blonde: No Time To Sleep
name_original: Jane Blonde: No Time To Sleep
description: The player is Jane Blonde.  Blonde wakes up as prisoner in Fort Knox - she has been captured.  Blonde must escape Fort Knox to save her life.  Fort Knox is filled with enemies that Blonde must evade or kill to escape.  There’s a catch - Blonde is extremely sleepy (due to being shot with a sleep dart).  So as Blonde escapes she must ensure her caffeine levels stay above 0, otherwise she will fall asleep and fail her escape.
